OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,FA row has broken out over the number
OL,7,Fof people sleeping rough on the
OL,8,Fstreets of Exeter.
OL,10,FThe city council says there are
OL,11,Fcurrently 11 people affected but one
OL,12,Fhomelessness charity says the method
OL,13,Fbeing used to count those on the
OL,14,Fstreets means the local authority has
OL,15,Funderestimated the scale of the issue.
OL,17,FThe figures come from a count carried
OL,18,Fout on the night of the 11th to 12th
OL,19,FNovember 2024.
