OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,FBut local charity St Petrock's said
OL,7,Ftheir own analysis on the day after
OL,8,Fthe count indicates the figure was
OL,9,Fapproximately 24.
OL,11,FOne local resident in Exeter said:
OL,12,F"There is a significant number of
OL,13,Frough sleepers. I've lived in Exeter
OL,14,Ffor 20 years and it's definitely been
OL,15,Fincreasing over that time.
OL,17,FAnother added: "We've got such a
OL,18,Fbeautiful city and it's blighted by
OL,19,Fsleeping bags near the Guildhall,
OL,20,Foutside the Cathedral. All our places
OL,21,Fof interest and beauty are marred."
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@POU}D@cO]
