OL,6,FOne person who has experienced
OL,7,Fsleeping rough in the city is Becca.
OL,8,FShe is now in night time accommodation
OL,9,Fand has said she believes this is
OL,10,Fthanks to the city's "really good
OL,11,Fhousing officer".
OL,13,FShe said: "I think she's really good
OL,14,Ffor our housing team in Exeter, she
OL,15,Fhelps as much as she can. She walks
OL,16,Faround this street every day to look
OL,17,Ffor homeless people so she tries her
OL,18,Fbest."
OL,26,@zD@FO]
