OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,FSt Petrock's said it believes that the
OL,7,Fextent of rough sleeping is
OL,8,Fconsistently underestimated by the
OL,9,Fmethodology used by Exeter City
OL,10,FCouncil and this year the scale of
OL,11,Funder-reporting is so great that it
OL,12,Fhas decided to publicly call on the
OL,13,Fcouncil to change the methodology it
OL,14,Fuses.
OL,16,FPeter Stephenson, Chief Executive of
OL,17,FSt Petrock's said: "The City Council
OL,18,Fhas for many years opted for a
OL,19,Fphysical count where teams scour the
OL,20,Fcity and count the number of rough
OL,21,Fsleepers found on a given night.
OL,26,@yD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
