OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,F"It is well known that some people
OL,7,Fsleeping rough, particularly women,
OL,8,Fconceal themselves well for their
OL,9,Fpersonal safety, or stay up all night
OL,10,Fto keep safe. As those doing the count
OL,11,Fwon't see these people, or when they
OL,12,Fsee them they won't be bedded down,
OL,13,Fthen they are not counted even though
OL,14,FCouncil officers and charities
OL,15,Fsupporting homeless people know they
OL,16,Fare sleeping rough."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@TO]
