OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,FMr Stephenson added "To be clear, St
OL,7,FPetrock's isn't suggesting our
OL,8,Fcolleagues at the City Council or
OL,9,Fanyone else is deliberately
OL,10,Fmanipulating the figures. But the fact
OL,11,Fof the matter is that basing rough
OL,12,Fsleeper numbers on a physical count
OL,13,Fusing the MHCLG (Ministry for Housing,
OL,14,FCommunities and Local Government)
OL,15,Fmethodology consistently
OL,16,Funderestimates the actual level of
OL,17,Frough sleeping in the city year after
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,26,@nD@UOUuD@QpmvD@apn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
