OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,F"This year, the snapshot count didn't
OL,7,Feven account for half of those we know
OL,8,Fwere sleeping rough that night and so
OL,9,Fbears no resemblance to reality."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Exeter City Council
OL,12,Fsaid: "The annual snapshot count
OL,13,Fmethod used is one of a number of
OL,14,Fagreed methods of recording rough
OL,15,Fsleeping from the Ministry for Housing
OL,16,FCommunities and Local Government. We
OL,17,Fhave used this method for several
OL,18,Fyears and it is also used by
OL,19,Fneighbouring authorities.
OL,26,@qD@aO]tD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
