PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1741378221
OL,3,CRow breaks out over number of rough
OL,4,Csleepers on the streets
OL,6,F"We don't rely on the annual count to
OL,7,Fdetermine need and responses to rough
OL,8,Fsleeping. In addition, we undertake a
OL,9,Fweekly count of rough sleepers using
OL,10,Fintelligence provided by our partners
OL,11,Fincluding St Petrock's.
OL,13,F"We are happy to use both
OL,14,Fmethodologies alongside each other for
OL,15,Fthe annual snapshot count in 2025, and
OL,16,Fif proved useful, in future years."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@cO]
